Title: 🌟🌟🌟🚀[ANN][ICO]🌟GET 3 TOKENS FOR 1🌟—Nimfamoney—CRYPTOLENDING PLATFORM
Body: Dear Miner2525,  Great question!  Nimfamoney does't provide a borrower with a loan directly. What we do is opening a positon on Nimfamoney with 300% funds from all NIMFA tokens a person has.  Let's say someone has 1000 NIMFA ($1000) and he gets a cryptoloan: 3000 NIMFA ($3000). Then he can get Bitcoins, Ethers and other cryptocurrencies with this loan but a person can withdraw to his own wallet only the part of funds that is more than $3000.  So if BTC raises to $6000, a person can withdraw to his wallet $3000 and payback the 3000 NIMFA ($3000) loan.  Does it make sense?  Max, Nimfamoney Founder & CEO

It means they can know nothing about margin call. We give 300% funds to anyone in just minutes. No need to waste weeks and months to dig deep into margin call and other complicated trading procesess.  QUESTION ABOUT MONEY PROTECTION: Imagine that a person gets 1000 NIMFA tokens ($5 = 1 NIMFA) on ICO and takes a 300% loan: 3000 NIMFA (=$15000). He uses this loan to buy ETH and BTC. But if the principal's amount value (2000 NIMFA) goes lower than 2000 NIMFA we'll automatically transfer principal amount to 100% decentralized cryptolending fund in order to protect it's value.  QUESTION ABOUT ICOs AND SCAM: We will strictly filter the ICOs that a person would have a chance to participate in with his loan.  QUESTION ABOUT SECURITY: We'll start Nimfamoney cryptocurrency lending process from easy steps and will be making it more efficient with the time. However the whole system that Nimfamoney would build on it's smart contracts will be as much secure as possible   Max, Nimfamoney Founder & CEO
